        "url": "/quotes/vladimir_horowitz_176219",
        "quote": "I must tell you I take terrible risks. Because my playing is very clear, when I make a mistake you hear it. If you want me to play only the notes without any specific dynamics, I will never make one mistake. Never be afraid to dare.",
