    {
        "url": "/quotes/vladimir_horowitz_802953",
        "quote": "Scriabin, as you know, is a mystic composer. His music is supersensuous, superromantic, and supermysterious. Everything is super; it is all a little overboard. Anyway, my parents were pleased that I played for him.",
