        "url": "/quotes/vladimir_horowitz_802956",
        "quote": "Scriabin slept with Chopin under his pillow, and I slept with Wagner under mine. I could not concentrate on memorizing Bach fugues, but I had all of 'Gotterdammerung' in my fingers.",
